1
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:08,617
♫ I want to go to the future ♫

2
00:00:08,617 --> 00:00:12,072
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,072 --> 00:00:18,265
♫ I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head ♫

4
00:00:18,265 --> 00:00:24,491
♫ I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do ♫

5
00:00:24,491 --> 00:00:30,712
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:30,712 --> 00:00:35,998
♫ We are always looking forward to the unknown future ♫

7
00:00:35,998 --> 00:00:43,298
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,298 --> 00:00:48,322
♫ Every day my heart beats for you ♫

9
00:00:48,322 --> 00:00:49,835
♫ Be your light ♫

10
00:00:49,835 --> 00:00:55,698
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,698 --> 00:01:02,098
♫ Every day the sun shines through the window ♫

12
00:01:02,098 --> 00:01:08,665
♫ With the reflection of you being my incredible highlight ♫

13
00:01:08,665 --> 00:01:11,736
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:13,219 --> 00:01:17,739
What's going on with this? What are you guys doing?

15
00:01:17,739 --> 00:01:23,899
Squeaking like two big monkeys in front of so many schoolmates! Is that a good influence?

16
00:01:24,859 --> 00:01:27,740
Principal Jin, you have no idea. It was such a dangerous situation.

17
00:01:27,740 --> 00:01:31,899
They were right next to the fountain. If I fall into it, I'm telling you...

18
00:01:31,899 --> 00:01:34,279
Good thing I have good agility, I...

19
00:01:34,279 --> 00:01:38,499
Don't be angry, Vice Principal. It was my fault for not keeping the students in order.

20
00:01:38,499 --> 00:01:40,446
Wipe it.

21
00:01:46,300 --> 00:01:50,587
What's going on with you two? Eager to go to Heaven?

22
00:01:51,259 --> 00:01:53,209
Who started it?

23
00:01:54,380 --> 00:01:56,599
Dong Dawei, was it you?

24
00:01:57,139 --> 00:02:01,820
You had a fight in the soccer team. Now you're not on the team, and you're still fighting! What do you want?

25
00:02:01,820 --> 00:02:06,299
Excuse me, Principal. I... I started it. It has nothing to do with Dawei.

26
00:02:06,299 --> 00:02:09,919
If you need to record a demerit or give out any punishments, I'll take them all.

27
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:12,400
I'll take responsibility for my own actions.

28
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:15,939
Oh, My. Tough guy, huh?

29
00:02:15,939 --> 00:02:18,480
Why don't you go be a hero on the Marshes of Mount Liang?
(T/N: reference to the classic novel "Water Margin")

30
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:19,980
I could.

31
00:02:19,980 --> 00:02:21,980
What did you say?

32
00:02:23,559 --> 00:02:27,560
This is your student? This is how you discipline them?

33
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,740
Behave.

34
00:02:28,740 --> 00:02:31,500
Old Jin, this is the child of our teaching staff.

35
00:02:31,500 --> 00:02:35,300
That's such a bad influence. We must handle this seriously.

36
00:02:42,090 --> 00:02:46,060
Gao Yang, don't think I can't discipline you if you're about to leave.

37
00:02:46,060 --> 00:02:48,880
Principal, please give him another chance.

38
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:50,619
It's okay, Mr. Wu.

39
00:02:50,619 --> 00:02:53,700
I can't bear to leave Dong. I just want to say goodbye to him.

40
00:02:53,700 --> 00:02:56,740
Our ceremony just got a bit out of hand.

41
00:02:58,059 --> 00:03:00,900
What's with your glib tongue?

42
00:03:01,980 --> 00:03:05,899
Here's the deal. You two, write a self-criticism letter.

43
00:03:05,899 --> 00:03:09,580
At least 5,000 words! Next week, you'll read it in front of the entire school!

44
00:03:09,580 --> 00:03:14,520
How was it? Was I really valiant and brave when I protected Gao Yang?

45
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:16,159
I'm a heroine!

46
00:03:16,159 --> 00:03:20,139
Beibei, you were so reckless. How dare you chase after Dong Dawei?

47
00:03:20,139 --> 00:03:26,139
What do you know? I don't care if he's Dong Dawei or Zhang Dawei. I'll smack anyone who bullies Gao Yang!

48
00:03:27,059 --> 00:03:32,659
Beibei, you're not sad about Gao Yang going to Beijing anymore?

49
00:03:42,219 --> 00:03:44,479
Do you think

50
00:03:45,599 --> 00:03:49,339
anyone would protect him like us

51
00:03:50,140 --> 00:03:53,120
if he gets bullied in Beijing?

52
00:03:55,740 --> 00:03:58,346
If you have other questions, I'll explain them to you next time.

53
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:05,160
Xiaowen, do you think Gao Yang is okay?

54
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:07,460
He hasn't been back for two classes.

55
00:04:07,460 --> 00:04:12,704
Why are you worried about someone who instigates a fight all the time?

56
00:04:12,704 --> 00:04:17,160
Because I don't think he's a bad boy.

57
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:19,899
Why do you say that?

58
00:04:19,899 --> 00:04:21,679
You... you don't understand.

59
00:04:21,679 --> 00:04:23,646
I don't understand what?

60
00:04:44,830 --> 00:04:48,909
Mi Jia, don't read letters from other people.

61
00:04:48,909 --> 00:04:50,999
Just read mine.

62
00:04:53,290 --> 00:04:57,439
Why are you so quiet all the time? Are you shy?

63
00:04:57,439 --> 00:05:00,172
Be my friend and I'll bring you to do something fun.

64
00:05:00,900 --> 00:05:02,812
Let me read it for you.

65
00:05:06,900 --> 00:05:14,140
"Dear Mi Jia, do you know what's the most intoxicating?

66
00:05:14,140 --> 00:05:16,839
Forever and always be with you."

67
00:05:16,839 --> 00:05:18,957
Not bad.

68
00:05:18,957 --> 00:05:21,460
Gao Yang. What are you doing?

69
00:05:21,460 --> 00:05:24,979
You're not in our class. It's none of your business.

70
00:05:27,140 --> 00:05:29,025
Go back to your seat.

71
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:39,440
It has nothing to do with me, huh? Do you know who Mi Jia is to me?

72
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:40,959
What did he call you?

73
00:05:40,959 --> 00:05:42,160
No, no.

74
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,879
Didn't I tell him not to harass you?

75
00:05:43,879 --> 00:05:47,979
N-N-No... L-L-Let me finish.

76
00:05:47,979 --> 00:05:50,439
Listen up, Class 2.

77
00:05:50,439 --> 00:05:54,880
Mi Jia is my... little sister.

78
00:05:57,160 --> 00:06:01,179
She came to our school to study for college, understand?

79
00:06:01,179 --> 00:06:04,940
If anyone harasses her and writes these disgusting things to her again,

80
00:06:04,940 --> 00:06:07,680
I'll take them all to the Principal's house tomorrow!

81
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:11,619
Who are you trying to threaten? Do you know where the principal lives?

82
00:06:11,619 --> 00:06:13,511
Above my place.

83
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:21,060
T-T-Thank you.

84
00:06:21,060 --> 00:06:23,419
Don't worry about it, it's nothing.

85
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:32,760
Since then, no one harassed me again.

86
00:06:37,539 --> 00:06:44,440
Actually, Gao Yang and Mr. Gao are both really nice.

87
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:50,270
[Episode 8: Parting Memories]

88
00:06:56,839 --> 00:06:58,401
Dong,

89
00:07:00,339 --> 00:07:02,039
I'm sorry.

90
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,820
Are you insane?

91
00:07:04,820 --> 00:07:09,079
I wanted to ask you to fight off campus. You refused.

92
00:07:09,079 --> 00:07:10,600
I'll deal with you another day.

93
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:13,339
Look, you can't bear to part with me.

94
00:07:13,339 --> 00:07:17,439
When I go to Beijing, you can't beat me up even if you want to.

95
00:07:19,879 --> 00:07:24,010
What? You're really going to Beijing?

96
00:07:25,580 --> 00:07:28,064
My mom is transferring me to a school there.

97
00:07:30,500 --> 00:07:32,139
Not bad.

98
00:07:32,879 --> 00:07:35,020
You're pretty lucky.

99
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:42,880
Your mom... is pretty rich?

100
00:07:42,880 --> 00:07:44,884
She's all right.

101
00:07:44,884 --> 00:07:51,600
She just earns a few dozen times more than Gao Bin.

102
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:53,940
Well, make sure your mom keeps you in check.

103
00:07:53,940 --> 00:07:55,615
Yes,

104
00:07:57,099 --> 00:08:00,800
without my mom, I wouldn't be alive now.

105
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:06,182
Does Gao Bin

106
00:08:07,060 --> 00:08:09,343
treat you badly?

107
00:08:09,343 --> 00:08:13,719
You spent a lot of time with him too. What do you think about him?

108
00:08:20,900 --> 00:08:23,419
Don't be so annoying in Beijing.

109
00:08:23,419 --> 00:08:26,980
You'd be pretty lonely after I leave.

110
00:08:27,700 --> 00:08:29,228
Go away.

111
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:38,600
Well, can I ask you a favor?

112
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:40,426
Go on.

113
00:08:40,426 --> 00:08:44,340
After I go to Beijing, don't bully Xiaowen and the others.

114
00:08:44,340 --> 00:08:46,639
Why should I listen to you?

115
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:54,280
If you're still mad, come see me in Beijing or wait until I come back.

116
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:57,839
They are not Gao Bin's sons. I am.

117
00:09:00,260 --> 00:09:02,579
Can you promise me?

118
00:09:02,579 --> 00:09:07,060
Gao Yang! What did you do this time? Can't you stay out of trouble for once?

119
00:09:07,060 --> 00:09:08,440
Dawei.

120
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:10,639
Can you promise me?

121
00:09:11,150 --> 00:09:13,340
What are you up to now?

122
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:48,840
Your back, your back. Lift up your butt.

123
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:51,399
Your posture isn't right. Do one more.

124
00:09:58,870 --> 00:10:00,220
Gao Yang,

125
00:10:00,220 --> 00:10:03,039
you're quite something.

126
00:10:04,260 --> 00:10:07,400
I was lectured by the Vice Principal after I was lectured by Principal Jin.

127
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:10,880
After that, Wu Dibao lectured me again.

128
00:10:11,430 --> 00:10:13,290
What were you thinking?

129
00:10:13,290 --> 00:10:16,400
You're just going to Beijing. Do you think you're above all now?

130
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:18,705
You just had to put me through hell, huh?

131
00:10:23,299 --> 00:10:26,239
Actually, it's not really your fault.

132
00:10:26,239 --> 00:10:29,000
It's your mom's fault. You're already a sophomore.

133
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:33,079
You only have one year before the college entrance exam. She just had to stir up trouble at such a critical moment.

134
00:10:33,079 --> 00:10:36,760
If you go to Beijing now, will you focus on your studies?

135
00:10:36,760 --> 00:10:39,279
I just want to go to Beijing.

136
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:44,340
If you want to go, keep doing push-ups!

137
00:10:44,340 --> 00:10:47,620
- Fine, I'll do it!
- Don't stop. Faster, faster!

138
00:10:47,620 --> 00:10:49,419
- Continue!
- I'll do it then.

139
00:10:49,419 --> 00:10:51,579
Mr. Gao, why don't we eat dinner first?

140
00:10:51,579 --> 00:10:53,640
Xiaowen, stay out of this.

141
00:10:53,640 --> 00:10:58,200
I have to punish him. He made me a fool in front of the whole school! I can't spoil him!

142
00:11:01,620 --> 00:11:03,020
Gao Yang, listen up.

143
00:11:03,020 --> 00:11:07,899
From now on, you'll come straight home after school. You can't go anywhere!

144
00:11:12,030 --> 00:11:13,519
What?

145
00:11:13,519 --> 00:11:16,579
Did I let you get up? Did you finish yet?

146
00:11:16,579 --> 00:11:21,200
Gao Bin, I'm going to Beijing. I'll live with my mom! You can't do anything about it!

147
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,699
Don't ever come back then!

148
00:11:22,699 --> 00:11:25,165
- Gao Yang!
- Don't go after him!

149
00:11:31,179 --> 00:11:32,810
Let's eat.

150
00:11:40,812 --> 00:11:43,432
♫ The white city ♫

151
00:11:43,432 --> 00:11:47,465
♫ The gray wallpaper ♫

152
00:11:47,465 --> 00:11:55,225
♫ The night sky after shooting stars have left ♫

153
00:11:55,225 --> 00:12:02,025
♫ The warm shadows fading in the night ♫

154
00:12:02,025 --> 00:12:09,865
♫ We laugh and ramble about so many interesting things in our future ♫

155
00:12:09,865 --> 00:12:16,985
♫ The wasted times we went through together ♫

156
00:12:16,985 --> 00:12:24,309
♫ Nobody else were there, only us, and that's why it's so beautiful♫

157
00:12:24,309 --> 00:12:30,624
♫ If you were to ask me where my future would be ♫

158
00:12:30,624 --> 00:12:34,600
Xiaowen, just let him be. Come on. Let's eat dinner first.

159
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:37,683
The food is getting cold. Don't save him anything.

160
00:12:39,100 --> 00:12:41,254
Come on, let's eat.

161
00:12:46,579 --> 00:12:49,519
Mr. Gao, I should go look for him.

162
00:12:49,519 --> 00:12:51,516
Let him be.

163
00:12:52,675 --> 00:12:58,845
♫ What I want is the story to stop where it should stop♫

164
00:12:58,845 --> 00:13:04,425
♫ Far away and stupidly ♫

165
00:13:04,425 --> 00:13:10,405
♫ Staring but refraining ♫

166
00:13:21,759 --> 00:13:24,120
How do you know I'm here?

167
00:13:27,179 --> 00:13:32,120
I saw you sitting here when I jogged with Mi Jia before.

168
00:13:49,380 --> 00:13:52,059
What you did for Mi Jia, thank you.

169
00:13:52,059 --> 00:13:53,836
What did I do?

170
00:13:53,836 --> 00:13:55,681
The love letters.

171
00:13:56,500 --> 00:14:00,000
That's nothing. It's a piece of cake.

172
00:14:02,100 --> 00:14:03,960
I thought you and Mi Jia...

173
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:05,860
Don't worry.

174
00:14:05,860 --> 00:14:07,960
I won't pursue her.

175
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:11,180
I know you two grew up together.

176
00:14:11,180 --> 00:14:15,360
You want to protect her. That's all I can do for you.

177
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:19,719
After I leave, you'll be on your own.

178
00:14:19,719 --> 00:14:22,399
- You still want to leave?
- I have to.

179
00:14:22,399 --> 00:14:25,284
Gao Bin... he can't keep me here.

180
00:14:26,679 --> 00:14:30,260
You don't want to leave him with a good impression before you leave?

181
00:14:32,299 --> 00:14:36,879
We've lived together for years. Why won't he leave me a good impression?

182
00:14:41,900 --> 00:14:45,399
Buy me the one with chives and egg filling next time.

183
00:14:54,225 --> 00:14:56,100
[Principal's Office]

184
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:59,440
"I deeply regret fighting in school,

185
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:02,559
but I'm just a child who longs to see his mother.

186
00:15:02,559 --> 00:15:07,600
If Gao Bin won't let me go to Beijing, I can't guarantee what I'll do in the future.

187
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:09,419
Sincerely, Gao Yang."

188
00:15:09,419 --> 00:15:12,480
Old Jin, look at this. Is this a self-criticism letter?

189
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:16,399
Vice Principal. Gao Yang... those are angry words. I'll just make him write another one later.

190
00:15:16,399 --> 00:15:18,900
Angry words? I'm still angry.

191
00:15:18,900 --> 00:15:22,299
If I overstate this, this is a threat to the school.

192
00:15:22,299 --> 00:15:26,899
Mr. Gao, Gao Yang is your son. You tell me what we should do.

193
00:15:26,899 --> 00:15:30,399
I'll abide by your decision. Anyway, I'm not letting him go to Beijing.

194
00:15:30,399 --> 00:15:35,059
Bin, Gao Yang is determined to leave.

195
00:15:35,059 --> 00:15:37,039
His mom agreed, too.

196
00:15:37,039 --> 00:15:41,240
If you do that, it will only be counterproductive. Do you know that?

197
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:45,300
Exactly. Even if he doesn't go to class, the other students need to go to class.

198
00:15:45,300 --> 00:15:49,399
Besides, don't forget you're a teacher. You have to set an example.

199
00:15:49,399 --> 00:15:52,900
Don't always let your personal affairs affect the school.

200
00:15:52,900 --> 00:15:58,020
About Gao Yang's behavior, it's all my fault. Sorry to trouble everyone.

201
00:15:59,579 --> 00:16:01,899
I'll accept any punishment from the school.

202
00:16:01,899 --> 00:16:04,179
You can deduct my pay for what Gao Yang cannot afford.

203
00:16:04,179 --> 00:16:05,969
However,

204
00:16:07,059 --> 00:16:09,600
Gao Yang is my son.

205
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:11,899
I won't let him leave.

206
00:16:12,779 --> 00:16:14,340
Don't worry about it.

207
00:16:14,340 --> 00:16:17,379
- Bin.
- Wait... What do you mean?

208
00:16:17,379 --> 00:16:20,520
- Principal Jin.
- I'll go convince him. I'll go convince him.

209
00:16:22,519 --> 00:16:24,039
Old Jin, look at that.

210
00:16:24,039 --> 00:16:28,639
Old Fu, come on. Take a seat. Here, have some tea. Calm down.

211
00:16:28,639 --> 00:16:31,209
[Relax Bar]

212
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:37,660
Come on.

213
00:16:43,420 --> 00:16:45,900
You don't need to drink it all. What are you doing?

214
00:16:47,260 --> 00:16:49,328
Come on, I'll pour you another one.

215
00:16:50,510 --> 00:16:55,790
Old Wu, I know why you're here. Did Jin ask you to come?

216
00:16:56,700 --> 00:17:00,180
It doesn't matter what you say. I won't let Gao Yang leave.

217
00:17:00,180 --> 00:17:02,717
I won't say anything. What can I say?

218
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:06,119
Let me tell you, Bin,

219
00:17:06,780 --> 00:17:10,440
we've been colleagues for so many years. I really admire you.

220
00:17:10,440 --> 00:17:13,580
You got married and had a child early.

221
00:17:13,580 --> 00:17:17,289
I don't even have a girlfriend yet and you're already divorced.

222
00:17:19,620 --> 00:17:21,540
Is that admiration or mockery?

223
00:17:21,540 --> 00:17:26,640
What I mean is, I only realize how hard it is to be a father when I look at you.

224
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:31,059
I'm telling you, Gao Yang is harder to discipline than a whole class of students.

225
00:17:31,059 --> 00:17:34,210
Besides, I also understand why you won't let Gao Yang go to Beijing.

226
00:17:34,210 --> 00:17:39,660
You're just afraid he won't be able to adapt and it'll affect his studies and his scores for the college entrance exam, right?

227
00:17:40,939 --> 00:17:45,140
See, everyone understands that. Why can't Gao Yang understand?

228
00:17:45,140 --> 00:17:47,140
Bin, you have to think of it this way.

229
00:17:47,140 --> 00:17:51,019
He's seventeen. He has his own ideas.

230
00:17:51,019 --> 00:17:53,019
Why do you think he wants to go to Beijing?

231
00:17:53,019 --> 00:17:57,119
He wants some maternal love before he becomes an adult.

232
00:17:57,119 --> 00:17:59,540
If you don't let him go to Beijing, what does that make you?

233
00:17:59,540 --> 00:18:03,219
You would deprive him of the chance to get in touch with his mom.

234
00:18:03,219 --> 00:18:07,219
I'm telling you, mom and dad are not the same.

235
00:18:07,219 --> 00:18:12,920
No matter how hard we try, the love you can provide cannot compare to that of his mother.

236
00:18:12,920 --> 00:18:17,080
I understand what you're saying. But Anna isn't an ordinary woman.

237
00:18:17,080 --> 00:18:20,219
Even if Gao Yang goes to Beijing, he won't get much maternal love.

238
00:18:20,219 --> 00:18:23,939
Bin, about that, you have to consider it from Gao Yang's perspective.

239
00:18:23,939 --> 00:18:26,093
He's lacking something.

240
00:18:26,580 --> 00:18:29,119
When you just got divorced, I was rather young at the time.

241
00:18:29,119 --> 00:18:31,739
Whenever you were busy, you would leave Gao Yang with me.

242
00:18:31,739 --> 00:18:34,060
He was so naughty at the time. He never stopped jumping up and down.

243
00:18:34,060 --> 00:18:37,320
To make him sit quietly for a while, I told him to write an essay.

244
00:18:37,320 --> 00:18:40,179
I said, "Write it now. You can choose your own topic. Write about anything."

245
00:18:40,179 --> 00:18:41,939
He finally stayed quiet for a while.

246
00:18:41,939 --> 00:18:45,560
When I came back in a while, do you know what he wrote about?

247
00:18:46,820 --> 00:18:48,920
"My Mom."

248
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:57,540
Bin, this is the right time for you to make it up to him,

249
00:18:58,060 --> 00:18:59,680
right?

250
00:19:06,690 --> 00:19:09,019
Yes, I'm not married and I don't have kids.

251
00:19:09,019 --> 00:19:13,460
But I think being a father is just like being a teacher.

252
00:19:13,460 --> 00:19:16,280
We are sending students away each year.

253
00:19:16,280 --> 00:19:18,415
What's our purpose in the end?

254
00:19:19,100 --> 00:19:23,259
It's the calling of the heart. It's the devotion of love.

255
00:19:23,259 --> 00:19:27,439
It's a spring breeze upon the world. It's the fountain of life.

256
00:19:27,439 --> 00:19:31,040
It's good enough to see the children grow up, make good achievements,

257
00:19:31,040 --> 00:19:34,280
and have a nice future, right?

258
00:19:41,630 --> 00:19:44,410
[No. 3 Tian Yuan Staff Accomodation]

259
00:20:02,019 --> 00:20:05,680
Mr. Gao, why are you here?

260
00:20:28,019 --> 00:20:33,340
Mr. Gao, if you're reluctant to see him leave,

261
00:20:33,340 --> 00:20:35,979
you should tell him in person.

262
00:21:05,060 --> 00:21:11,319
Beibei, don't be too upset about Gao Yang's departure. We can also call each other after school.

263
00:21:19,259 --> 00:21:21,919
Beibei, I...

264
00:21:23,259 --> 00:21:24,380
Do you want a torch ice-cream?

265
00:21:24,380 --> 00:21:29,340
Jiabao, it'll just be the two of us...

266
00:21:30,259 --> 00:21:32,580
after Gao Yang leaves.

267
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:35,410
I...

268
00:21:37,419 --> 00:21:40,240
Isn't he a disloyal friend?

269
00:21:40,240 --> 00:21:42,600
He's a jerk!

270
00:21:42,600 --> 00:21:47,580
Well, Gao Yang is actually pretty nice.

271
00:21:47,580 --> 00:21:49,699
Don't say that about him.

272
00:21:50,380 --> 00:21:54,940
How is he nice? He eats your food, hogs your things, spends your money,

273
00:21:54,940 --> 00:21:57,440
and makes fun of me all the time.

274
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:59,519
He...

275
00:22:01,300 --> 00:22:05,799
Did you forget? He introduced us to each other.

276
00:22:05,799 --> 00:22:08,640
[Happy Birthday to Beibei]

277
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:12,939
This is my buddy Jiabao. This is my close female friend Beibei.

278
00:22:12,939 --> 00:22:16,255
From now on, the three of us will be good friends.

279
00:22:16,255 --> 00:22:18,534
Why are you so short?

280
00:22:18,534 --> 00:22:21,100
Eat more cake later. It will help you grow taller.

281
00:22:21,100 --> 00:22:23,079
Come on. Let's celebrate my birthday!

282
00:22:23,079 --> 00:22:25,240
Gao Yang, give me back my crown!

283
00:22:25,240 --> 00:22:27,820
♪ Happy birthday to me ♪

284
00:22:27,820 --> 00:22:33,460
It's my birthday, not yours! Gao Yang, give me back my crown!

285
00:22:34,259 --> 00:22:38,039
Gao Yang was so nice to us. Did you forget?

286
00:22:38,820 --> 00:22:43,740
I'm upset because I remember all of that.

287
00:22:47,300 --> 00:22:50,699
Beibei, take a bite. The torch is melting.

288
00:22:52,580 --> 00:22:54,820
Zhao Jiabao, I made a decision.

289
00:22:54,820 --> 00:22:57,420
Even if he's leaving, we have to make him feel guilty!

290
00:22:57,420 --> 00:23:00,168
Otherwise, it would be a waste of our friendship over the years!

291
00:23:10,060 --> 00:23:13,756
Three notebooks, they're brand new. I've never used them before.

292
00:23:16,580 --> 00:23:19,139
Oh, and this too. It's mosquito repellent.

293
00:23:19,139 --> 00:23:22,367
There are a lot of mosquitoes in Tieyuan in the summer. You can use it.

294
00:23:29,100 --> 00:23:31,259
This is awesome.

295
00:23:33,419 --> 00:23:36,680
It's all my savings, game cards.

296
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:40,439
There are a lot of new ones in there. You can have that too.

297
00:23:40,439 --> 00:23:42,614
You're not coming tomorrow?

298
00:23:42,614 --> 00:23:46,419
I'll take a few days off and my mom will take me to Beijing.

299
00:23:46,419 --> 00:23:48,400
Mr. Gao...

300
00:23:48,400 --> 00:23:50,137
What about him?

301
00:23:50,137 --> 00:23:52,759
He might have something to tell you.

302
00:23:52,759 --> 00:23:55,419
I don't have anything to say to him.

303
00:23:56,500 --> 00:24:00,620
By the way, you can use anything in my room.

304
00:24:00,620 --> 00:24:04,880
But you can't disassemble that bed. I'm still coming back during breaks.

305
00:24:10,879 --> 00:24:15,380
By the way, I have to teach you my secret codes with Beibei.

306
00:24:15,380 --> 00:24:17,472
What secret codes?

307
00:24:19,480 --> 00:24:22,919
This means... the small pocket in her backpack.

308
00:24:22,919 --> 00:24:26,019
This one means don't leave after school.

309
00:24:26,019 --> 00:24:28,180
This is the best. Here we go.

310
00:24:33,380 --> 00:24:34,963
What is it?

311
00:24:37,440 --> 00:24:39,960
Come with me.

312
00:24:40,620 --> 00:24:42,282
Hurry, come on.

313
00:24:47,210 --> 00:24:49,440
We're almost there. Hurry.

314
00:24:52,799 --> 00:24:56,199
Come on. This is it. Hurry.

315
00:24:58,599 --> 00:25:01,140
This gesture means there's something in here.

316
00:25:01,140 --> 00:25:03,620
You can put the answers inside when you go to the restroom during an exam.

317
00:25:03,620 --> 00:25:06,819
Beibei has terrible grades. You should help her more.

318
00:25:06,819 --> 00:25:08,860
Help her cheat?

319
00:25:09,939 --> 00:25:11,900
Don't be so straightforward.

320
00:25:11,900 --> 00:25:16,079
You can communicate your feelings with her through this space.

321
00:25:16,620 --> 00:25:20,220
Don't you think I'm a very loyal friend?

322
00:25:24,300 --> 00:25:26,265
After I leave,

323
00:25:27,259 --> 00:25:30,939
I worry about my friends the most.

324
00:25:30,939 --> 00:25:35,660
Jiabao always wants to write his stupid songs. His parents won't allow it.

325
00:25:35,660 --> 00:25:39,100
If he buys a CD or something, help him stash it away.

326
00:25:39,100 --> 00:25:43,779
As for Tian Meng, all she does is read and study. She doesn't know anything.

327
00:25:43,779 --> 00:25:46,780
Don't listen to any of her advice.

328
00:25:47,499 --> 00:25:49,920
Mi Jia...

329
00:25:50,519 --> 00:25:53,319
Y-Y-You... you're...

330
00:25:53,319 --> 00:25:55,259
Be serious.

331
00:25:57,060 --> 00:25:59,299
Right, and also Beibei.

332
00:25:59,299 --> 00:26:04,019
She's always yelling and following behind me like a crazy girl.

333
00:26:04,019 --> 00:26:09,019
After I leave, you should help her and set a life goal for her or something.

334
00:26:09,019 --> 00:26:10,380
Do you hear me?

335
00:26:10,380 --> 00:26:12,179
What about your dad?

336
00:26:12,179 --> 00:26:16,219
Why must you mention him? He's happy without me.

337
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:18,715
Remember.

338
00:26:27,750 --> 00:26:31,659
When did Beibei put this in? She didn't even tell me.

339
00:26:31,659 --> 00:26:33,920
So mysterious.

340
00:26:38,380 --> 00:26:41,040
Gao Yang, do you still remember?

341
00:26:41,040 --> 00:26:44,420
When you were 6 years old, your parents got a divorce.

342
00:26:44,420 --> 00:26:49,399
You hugged me so tight and refused to let go. You said you didn't want to leave Tieyuan and your friends.

343
00:26:49,399 --> 00:26:53,740
We had a deal. I always remember that.

344
00:26:54,250 --> 00:26:57,419
When we were in elementary school, our classmates made fun of me for eating Kimchi all the time.

345
00:26:57,419 --> 00:27:00,479
But you would fight me for it and you really loved it.

346
00:27:00,479 --> 00:27:03,060
Our classmates started to envy me.

347
00:27:03,060 --> 00:27:08,939
I still remember that now. At the time, I thought... I want to be with Gao Yang for the rest of my life.

348
00:27:08,939 --> 00:27:15,400
Over the years, I think I've been good to you. Our relationship isn't just an ordinary friendship, right?

349
00:27:15,400 --> 00:27:16,850
Gao Yang,

350
00:27:16,850 --> 00:27:22,319
you're going to abandon me for Beijing now. I just have one thing to say.

351
00:27:22,319 --> 00:27:25,699
You're a total idiot. Over.

352
00:27:27,780 --> 00:27:32,840
She... She made it sound so affectionate.

353
00:27:43,824 --> 00:27:47,338
♫ I want to find you ♫

354
00:27:47,338 --> 00:27:51,998
♫ Let me run to you ♫

355
00:27:51,998 --> 00:27:54,030
♫ Your laughters ♫

356
00:27:54,030 --> 00:27:59,190
♫ How much are left in my heart ♫

357
00:27:59,190 --> 00:28:05,106
♫ Another season has passed ♫

358
00:28:05,106 --> 00:28:08,259
The place we're going is called the Lake of Brotherhood.

359
00:28:08,259 --> 00:28:11,820
Rumor says the Leaders of the Eight Banners of the Qing Dynasty became sworn brothers there,

360
00:28:11,820 --> 00:28:15,610
just like the Oath of the Peach Garden. It's really famous.
(T/N: reference to the classic novel "Romance of the Three Kingdoms)

361
00:28:15,610 --> 00:28:22,080
♫ I found you, I also found myself ♫

362
00:28:22,080 --> 00:28:28,220
Gao Yang, you should be happy when we're on a field trip. Don't pull a long face.

363
00:28:28,220 --> 00:28:30,500
Do it for my sake, okay?

364
00:28:40,459 --> 00:28:45,319
Xiaowen, do you want to know a secret from Gao Yang's childhood?

365
00:28:45,319 --> 00:28:47,041
Sure.

366
00:28:47,041 --> 00:28:50,620
Gao Yang was a really smart child.

367
00:28:50,620 --> 00:28:56,559
I took him fishing once, and he flung his shoes into the river.

368
00:28:56,559 --> 00:29:01,579
I said, "I'll jump in to get them." Do you know how he replied?

369
00:29:01,579 --> 00:29:02,645
How?

370
00:29:02,645 --> 00:29:04,986
"You don't need to.

371
00:29:04,986 --> 00:29:09,719
Someone will fish them out with their fishing rods in a while."

372
00:29:22,620 --> 00:29:24,629
Let's listen to music.

373
00:29:49,450 --> 00:29:54,040
This is the famous Lake of Brotherhood!
[Lake of Brotherhood]

374
00:29:54,040 --> 00:29:58,259
What do you think? The scenery is beautiful, right?

375
00:29:58,259 --> 00:30:00,180
I don't see any scenery.

376
00:30:00,180 --> 00:30:02,467
I can only feel the wind.

377
00:30:02,467 --> 00:30:06,480
Mr. Gao, why are we the only ones

378
00:30:06,480 --> 00:30:08,860
at this famous Lake of Brotherhood?

379
00:30:08,860 --> 00:30:11,240
Because it's the off-season.

380
00:30:11,240 --> 00:30:13,050
Let's go.

381
00:30:13,050 --> 00:30:14,854
Let's set up the camp!

382
00:31:12,000 --> 00:31:14,100
Xiaowen, make it tight.

383
00:31:14,100 --> 00:31:15,720
Okay.

384
00:31:15,720 --> 00:31:18,280
Gao Yang, pull the ropes taut.

385
00:31:18,280 --> 00:31:22,029
- Tighten it or it will fly away again.
- Got it.

386
00:31:27,920 --> 00:31:29,960
You two, check it again.

387
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:31,800
I'll go build a fire.

388
00:31:31,800 --> 00:31:33,880
We'll eat sooner.

389
00:31:43,279 --> 00:31:45,820
I'll teach you a lesson today.

390
00:31:45,820 --> 00:31:50,540
When it comes to building a fire and surviving in the wild, you need certain techniques.

391
00:31:50,540 --> 00:31:52,549
Check this out.

392
00:32:03,440 --> 00:32:05,179
What are you doing?

393
00:32:05,179 --> 00:32:08,879
Use your technique. Why don't you use your technique?

394
00:32:09,839 --> 00:32:11,839
Stop embarrassing yourself. Let me do it.

395
00:32:11,839 --> 00:32:14,535
There's no technique for lighting a fire.

396
00:32:23,920 --> 00:32:26,568
- There's a problem with the lighter.
- That's right.

397
00:32:31,480 --> 00:32:33,759
That lighter doesn't work.

398
00:32:38,979 --> 00:32:40,957
We have fire!

399
00:32:53,820 --> 00:32:56,379
- Xiaowen, the ingredients.
- Okay.

400
00:33:29,259 --> 00:33:32,780
Gao Yang, stay away from the water. It's dangerous, understand?

401
00:33:32,780 --> 00:33:34,601
I'm really far from it.

402
00:33:58,739 --> 00:34:01,200
Coming! The grilled fish is ready.

403
00:34:01,200 --> 00:34:03,100
What a feast!

404
00:34:03,100 --> 00:34:04,699
What does it have to do with you?

405
00:34:04,699 --> 00:34:07,060
If it wasn't for Xiaowen, we would go hungry.

406
00:34:07,060 --> 00:34:08,639
Yes, yes.

407
00:34:08,639 --> 00:34:10,360
Thank you, Xiaowen!

408
00:34:10,360 --> 00:34:13,239
But we need something to go with the food.

409
00:34:14,519 --> 00:34:16,181
Want a drink?

410
00:34:18,559 --> 00:34:22,779
Tonight, the three brothers of Tieyuan

411
00:34:24,599 --> 00:34:27,960
are gathered here.

412
00:34:30,340 --> 00:34:34,175
The Lake of Brotherhood is all about brotherhood.

413
00:34:34,920 --> 00:34:37,119
- Let's drink to that!
- Forget it.

414
00:34:37,119 --> 00:34:40,999
Just drink if you want to. You don't have to rhyme.

415
00:34:40,999 --> 00:34:42,700
It's all about brotherhood.

416
00:34:42,700 --> 00:34:44,708
It's all about brotherhood.

417
00:34:50,820 --> 00:34:52,603
Let's eat.

418
00:35:03,660 --> 00:35:08,500
Gao Yang, do you still remember how long it's been since we last had an outing?

419
00:35:08,500 --> 00:35:11,181
Have we ever had one?

420
00:35:11,181 --> 00:35:14,440
This kid. You loved fishing when you were little.

421
00:35:14,440 --> 00:35:16,940
I love fishing? You love fishing.

422
00:35:16,940 --> 00:35:19,106
I was only there to accompany you.

423
00:35:20,539 --> 00:35:22,236
Sure, sure.

424
00:35:22,236 --> 00:35:24,380
Gao Yang, remember that time?

425
00:35:24,380 --> 00:35:25,359
- Do you still remember?
- Wait...

426
00:35:25,359 --> 00:35:27,570
- At the time, I—
- We're eating. Why are you talking so much?

427
00:35:27,570 --> 00:35:29,571
Just drink your beer.

428
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:36,601
The fire is dying. I'll go get some firewood.

429
00:35:36,601 --> 00:35:39,267
- I'll help you, Xiaowen.
- That's okay.

430
00:35:39,267 --> 00:35:40,878
What do you want?

431
00:35:45,820 --> 00:35:47,474
Yang,

432
00:35:48,180 --> 00:35:52,060
I want to have a heartfelt talk with you.

433
00:35:52,060 --> 00:35:53,777
Go on then.

434
00:35:54,880 --> 00:35:59,012
Well... I admit,

435
00:35:59,012 --> 00:36:03,099
I have done a lot of unreliable things over the years.

436
00:36:03,099 --> 00:36:04,780
I'm sorry about that.

437
00:36:04,780 --> 00:36:07,840
It's not too late to admit that now.

438
00:36:09,200 --> 00:36:11,559
What I want to say is...

439
00:36:13,300 --> 00:36:15,007
What?

440
00:36:15,559 --> 00:36:18,719
If you go to Beijing, I...

441
00:36:20,700 --> 00:36:22,778
What's wrong with Beijing?

442
00:36:27,979 --> 00:36:29,510
No...

443
00:36:30,839 --> 00:36:32,820
What exactly do you want to say? Just say it.

444
00:36:32,820 --> 00:36:34,559
I really think...

445
00:36:34,559 --> 00:36:36,640
What do you want to say?

446
00:36:37,900 --> 00:36:40,019
What are you getting at?

447
00:36:40,939 --> 00:36:44,678
Well... That tent is too small.

448
00:36:44,678 --> 00:36:46,600
It won't fit the three of us.

449
00:36:46,600 --> 00:36:48,619
I'll go sleep in the car.

450
00:36:48,619 --> 00:36:51,025
I'll go clean up.

451
00:36:51,025 --> 00:36:53,010
What is that?

452
00:37:51,370 --> 00:37:57,403
♫ I know the direction of dawn ♫

453
00:37:57,403 --> 00:38:04,768
♫ It's right in front of me ♫

454
00:38:04,768 --> 00:38:10,858
♫ Starlight shines along the way ♫

455
00:38:10,858 --> 00:38:16,798
♫ Accompanying me on my adventure ♫

456
00:38:16,798 --> 00:38:23,450
♫ I don't fear how rough the journey might be ♫

457
00:38:23,450 --> 00:38:29,090
♫ Maybe ♫

458
00:38:29,090 --> 00:38:33,077
♫ Go ♫

459
00:38:33,077 --> 00:38:36,425
♫ Set sail for your dreams ♫

460
00:38:36,425 --> 00:38:39,820
♫ Don't leave any regret in your youth ♫

461
00:38:39,820 --> 00:38:46,480
♫ Even if it hurts all over ♫

462
00:38:46,480 --> 00:38:49,791
♫ Find the answer through the crazies path ♫

463
00:38:49,791 --> 00:38:53,903
♫ Break the storm with the bravest heart ♫

464
00:38:53,903 --> 00:38:57,723
♫ I'll flap my wings to fly to the future ♫

465
00:38:57,723 --> 00:39:05,983
♫ And go straight forward without any sorrow ♫
